{"tid":781133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日ocamp啲女女濕曬","createTime":"2018-08-15T15:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T19:07:01.000Z","uid":152147,"like":2,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d51c6aaca1c516c9d5ed644048f5b48a15664973","tid":781133,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日就係ocamp嘅大日子 咁我琴晚都訓唔著 一樣凌晨3，4點起身gel到個頭會反光個隻 咁由於打完風都應該好撚熱 我就著件潮牌superme 就算<br />\n<br />\n咁組爸媽見到我已經話咩組仔高質個啲啦<br />\n我心諗 梗係啦 我張家輝身形 余文樂外貌 再加埋呢一把秀髮與陽光嘅裝扮<br />\n示意圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/234701_8a37284f7e6ad798ed0cd5cf6e1b14cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F234701_8a37284f7e6ad798ed0cd5cf6e1b14cb.png&h=745c8755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好快到city hunt 組爸話不如飲茶啦 咁啲組仔女都話好 我地就去左飲茶 <br />\n點撚知間茶樓 啲冷氣凍撚到仆街 搞到我係咁打黑痴 噴到對面啲女女濕曬 已經心知不妙 好再我仲有補獲機會 到埋單個下 我諗住拎張ae出黎找數 順便威返次 點撚知拎錯左張中學學生證出黎比個酒樓呀嬸 個呀嬸用佢啲唔咸唔淡嘅廣東話話 梨比乜撚野卡禾牙<br />\n個下我比人笑到面都黃 組爸仲一啖茶噴落啲組女組媽到 搞到未玩水game已經濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054968816c946b21fc1b1d87e06f40674d100047","tid":781133,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"邊撚個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9b86b1a31985e38fe7a9f44ca44a2f07f126ab","tid":781133,"uid":142144,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"好尷尬😅"},{"pid":"f410a656a4a3eac3f1b22af897ff8db0b967cf74","tid":781133,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"ff2b70e3b4eaeb2c1a3f359c74eae6833e72bec8","tid":781133,"uid":59218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:33:54.000Z","msg":"冷汗出哂緊係濕啦ching"},{"pid":"b2e0d4c6884c40d88524fb9d12ea6237c21db01d","tid":7811